==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Migrant
<hw>Mi"grant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
migratory bird, person, or other animal.</def></p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person who changes residence frequently in search
of employment, especially farm labor, such as harvesting crops
seasonally; also called <altname>migrant laborer</altname> or
<altname>migrant worker</altname>. Sometimes the migrant worker is not a
resident of the country in which the work is performed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Migrate</ent>⟦br⟧
